data.description: Prime location with this 4 bedroom, 4 bath home situated on a beautiful 1/2-acre corner lot with an additional paved parking area and privacy fenced section, multi-level decks, underground sprinkler system, and an attached oversized 2 car heated garage. Enjoy 3 levels of spacious living with almost 3,000 feet of living space which includes a generous sized family room, hardwood floors, Silestone counters and sinks, lower-level full bathroom, extra storage area, master with 2 walk in closets, and ensuite including a whirlpool tub and in floor heat.,Just a minute from Stettin Elementary school, minutes from shopping, Hwy 51, parks and more.
